{
  "video_id": "iWaZEXBbQL0",
  "title": "Maps that show us who we are (not just where we are) | Danny Dorling",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13120.0,
      "end_time": 17840.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like you to imagine the world anew."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17840.0,
      "end_time": 20039.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to show you some maps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20039.0,
      "end_time": 22800.0,
      "text": "which have been drawn by Ben Hennig,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22800.0,
      "end_time": 24520.0,
      "text": "of the planet in a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24520.0,
      "end_time": 30480.0,
      "text": "that most of you will never have seen the planet depicted before."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30480.0,
      "end_time": 34480.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s an image that you&#39;re very familiar with."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34480.0,
      "end_time": 38560.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m old enough that I was actually born before we saw this image."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38560.0,
      "end_time": 41160.0,
      "text": "Apparently some of my first words were &quot;moona, moona,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41160.0,
      "end_time": 44280.0,
      "text": "but I think that&#39;s my mom having a particular fantasy"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44280.0,
      "end_time": 46560.0,
      "text": "about what her baby boy could see"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46560.0,
      "end_time": 51680.0,
      "text": "on the flickering black and white TV screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51680.0,
      "end_time": 53320.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s only been a few centuries"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53320.0,
      "end_time": 58160.0,
      "text": "since we&#39;ve actually, most of us, thought of our planet as spherical."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58160.0,
      "end_time": 61240.0,
      "text": "When we first saw these images in the 1960s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61240.0,
      "end_time": 66320.0,
      "text": "the world was changing at an incredible rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66320.0,
      "end_time": 70600.0,
      "text": "In my own little discipline of human geography,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 70600.0,
      "end_time": 73360.0,
      "text": "a cartographer called Waldo Tobler"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73360.0,
      "end_time": 75920.0,
      "text": "was drawing new maps of the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 75920.0,
      "end_time": 77440.0,
      "text": "and these maps have now spread,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77440.0,
      "end_time": 80200.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to show you one of them now."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 80200.0,
      "end_time": 83720.0,
      "text": "This map is a map of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 83720.0,
      "end_time": 86160.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s a map which looks to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86160.0,
      "end_time": 88200.0,
      "text": "a little bit strange."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88200.0,
      "end_time": 92040.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a map in which we stretched places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92040.0,
      "end_time": 96760.0,
      "text": "so that those areas which contain many people are drawn larger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 96760.0,
      "end_time": 99720.0,
      "text": "and those areas, like the Sahara and the Himalayas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 99720.0,
      "end_time": 102760.0,
      "text": "in which there are few people, have been shrunk away."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102760.0,
      "end_time": 107120.0,
      "text": "Everybody on the planet is given an equal amount of space."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 107120.0,
      "end_time": 110680.0,
      "text": "The cities are shown shining bright."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 110680.0,
      "end_time": 114280.0,
      "text": "The lines are showing you submarine cables and trade routes."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 114280.0,
      "end_time": 117960.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s one particular line that goes from the Chinese port of Dalian"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117960.0,
      "end_time": 119680.0,
      "text": "through past Singapore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 119680.0,
      "end_time": 121440.0,
      "text": "through the Suez Canal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 121440.0,
      "end_time": 123800.0,
      "text": "through the Mediterranean and round to Rotterdam."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123800.0,
      "end_time": 125320.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s showing you the route"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 125320.0,
      "end_time": 129280.0,
      "text": "of what was the world&#39;s largest ship just a year ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129280.0,
      "end_time": 135320.0,
      "text": "a ship which was taking so many containers of goods"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 135320.0,
      "end_time": 137200.0,
      "text": "that when they were unloaded,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 137200.0,
      "end_time": 142680.0,
      "text": "if the lorries had all gone in convoy, they would have been 100 kilometers long."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 142680.0,
      "end_time": 145440.0,
      "text": "This is how our world is now connected."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 145440.0,
      "end_time": 151440.0,
      "text": "This is the quantity of stuff we are now moving around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 151440.0,
      "end_time": 154200.0,
      "text": "just on one ship, on one voyage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 154200.0,
      "end_time": 158320.0,
      "text": "in five weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 158320.0,
      "end_time": 161640.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve lived in cities for a very long time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 161640.0,
      "end_time": 163880.0,
      "text": "but most of us didn&#39;t live in cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 163880.0,
      "end_time": 167040.0,
      "text": "This is Çatalhöyük, one of the world&#39;s first cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 167040.0,
      "end_time": 171160.0,
      "text": "At its peak 9,000 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 171160.0,
      "end_time": 178080.0,
      "text": "people had to walk over the roofs of others&#39; houses to get to their home."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 178080.0,
      "end_time": 181400.0,
      "text": "If you look carefully at the map of the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 181400.0,
      "end_time": 184280.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll see it has no streets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 184280.0,
      "end_time": 187760.0,
      "text": "because streets are something we invented."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 187760.0,
      "end_time": 190000.0,
      "text": "The world changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 190000.0,
      "end_time": 193400.0,
      "text": "It changes by trial and error."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 193400.0,
      "end_time": 196320.0,
      "text": "We work out slowly and gradually"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 196320.0,
      "end_time": 199480.0,
      "text": "how to live in better ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 199480.0,
      "end_time": 205600.0,
      "text": "And the world has changed incredibly quickly most recently."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 205600.0,
      "end_time": 209560.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s only within the last six, seven, or eight generations"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 209560.0,
      "end_time": 213840.0,
      "text": "that we have actually realized that we are a species."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 213840.0,
      "end_time": 217240.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s only within the last few decades"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 217240.0,
      "end_time": 222240.0,
      "text": "that a map like this could be drawn."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 222240.0,
      "end_time": 227560.0,
      "text": "Again, the underlying map is the map of world population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 227560.0,
      "end_time": 233240.0,
      "text": "but over it, you&#39;re seeing arrows showing how we spread out of Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 233240.0,
      "end_time": 237040.0,
      "text": "with dates showing you where we think we arrived"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 237040.0,
      "end_time": 239680.0,
      "text": "at particular times."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 239680.0,
      "end_time": 243560.0,
      "text": "I have to redraw this map every few months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 243560.0,
      "end_time": 248560.0,
      "text": "because somebody makes a discovery that a particular date was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 248560.0,
      "end_time": 255600.0,
      "text": "We are learning about ourselves at an incredible speed."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 255600.0,
      "end_time": 258640.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 258640.0,
      "end_time": 260920.0,
      "text": "A lot of change is gradual."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 260920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262440.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s accretion."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 262440.0,
      "end_time": 265320.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t notice the change"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 265320.0,
      "end_time": 267160.0,
      "text": "because we only have short lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 267160.0,
      "end_time": 270560.0,
      "text": "70, 80, if you&#39;re lucky 90 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 270560.0,
      "end_time": 272600.0,
      "text": "This graph is showing you"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 272600.0,
      "end_time": 276120.0,
      "text": "the annual rate of population growth in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 276120.0,
      "end_time": 280080.0,
      "text": "It was very low until around about 1850,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 280080.0,
      "end_time": 282720.0,
      "text": "and then the rate of population growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 282720.0,
      "end_time": 284840.0,
      "text": "began to rise"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 284840.0,
      "end_time": 286880.0,
      "text": "so that around the time I was born,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 286880.0,
      "end_time": 292640.0,
      "text": "when we first saw those images from the moon of our planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 292640.0,
      "end_time": 297440.0,
      "text": "our global population was growing at two percent a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 297440.0,
      "end_time": 302600.0,
      "text": "If it had carried on growing at two percent a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 302600.0,
      "end_time": 306560.0,
      "text": "for just another couple of centuries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 306560.0,
      "end_time": 308840.0,
      "text": "the entire planet would be covered"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 308840.0,
      "end_time": 311920.0,
      "text": "with a seething mass of human bodies"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 311920.0,
      "end_time": 315000.0,
      "text": "all touching each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 315000.0,
      "end_time": 316840.0,
      "text": "And people were scared."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 316840.0,
      "end_time": 318680.0,
      "text": "They were scared of population growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 318680.0,
      "end_time": 322040.0,
      "text": "and what they called &quot;the population bomb&quot; in 1968."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 322040.0,
      "end_time": 325240.0,
      "text": "But then, if you look at the end of the graph,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 325240.0,
      "end_time": 328720.0,
      "text": "the growth began to slow."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 328720.0,
      "end_time": 330120.0,
      "text": "The decade --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 330120.0,
      "end_time": 333600.0,
      "text": "the &#39;70s, the &#39;80s, the &#39;90s, the noughties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 333600.0,
      "end_time": 336600.0,
      "text": "and in this decade, even faster --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 336600.0,
      "end_time": 338240.0,
      "text": "our population growth is slowing."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 338240.0,
      "end_time": 339520.0,
      "text": "Our planet is stabilizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 339520.0,
      "end_time": 342560.0,
      "text": "We are heading towards nine, 10, or 11 billion people"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 342560.0,
      "end_time": 344400.0,
      "text": "by the end of the century."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 344400.0,
      "end_time": 347760.0,
      "text": "Within that change, you can see tumult."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 347760.0,
      "end_time": 349600.0,
      "text": "You can see the Second World War."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 349600.0,
      "end_time": 353800.0,
      "text": "You can see the pandemic in 1918 from influenza."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 353800.0,
      "end_time": 356400.0,
      "text": "You can see the great Chinese famine."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 356400.0,
      "end_time": 358720.0,
      "text": "These are the events we tend to concentrate on."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 358720.0,
      "end_time": 362680.0,
      "text": "We tend to concentrate on the terrible events in the news."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 362680.0,
      "end_time": 366360.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t tend to concentrate on the gradual change"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 366360.0,
      "end_time": 369480.0,
      "text": "and the good news stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 369480.0,
      "end_time": 371200.0,
      "text": "We worry about people."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 371200.0,
      "end_time": 373480.0,
      "text": "We worry about how many people there are."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 373480.0,
      "end_time": 377200.0,
      "text": "We worry about how you can get away from people."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 377200.0,
      "end_time": 381760.0,
      "text": "But this is the map of the world changed again to make area large,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 381760.0,
      "end_time": 386160.0,
      "text": "the further away people are from each area."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 386160.0,
      "end_time": 390120.0,
      "text": "So if you want to know where to go to get away from everybody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 390120.0,
      "end_time": 392720.0,
      "text": "here&#39;s the best places to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 392720.0,
      "end_time": 395560.0,
      "text": "And every year, these areas get bigger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 395560.0,
      "end_time": 398840.0,
      "text": "because every year, we are coming off the land globally."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 398840.0,
      "end_time": 400320.0,
      "text": "We are moving into the cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 400320.0,
      "end_time": 402520.0,
      "text": "We are packing in more densely."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 402520.0,
      "end_time": 404160.0,
      "text": "There are wolves again in Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 404160.0,
      "end_time": 409200.0,
      "text": "and the wolves are moving west across the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 409200.0,
      "end_time": 412920.0,
      "text": "Our world is changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 412920.0,
      "end_time": 415680.0,
      "text": "You have worries."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 415680.0,
      "end_time": 420600.0,
      "text": "This is a map showing where the water falls on our planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 420600.0,
      "end_time": 422320.0,
      "text": "We now know that."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 422320.0,
      "end_time": 426120.0,
      "text": "And you can look at where Çatalhöyük was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 426120.0,
      "end_time": 428720.0,
      "text": "where three continents meet, Africa, Asia, and Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 428720.0,
      "end_time": 431720.0,
      "text": "and you can see there are a large number of people living there"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 431720.0,
      "end_time": 433320.0,
      "text": "in areas with very little water."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 433320.0,
      "end_time": 437040.0,
      "text": "And you can see areas in which there is a great deal of rainfall as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 437040.0,
      "end_time": 440440.0,
      "text": "And we can get a bit more sophisticated."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 440440.0,
      "end_time": 443840.0,
      "text": "Instead of making the map be shaped by people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 443840.0,
      "end_time": 446080.0,
      "text": "we can shape the map by water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 446080.0,
      "end_time": 447960.0,
      "text": "and then we can change it every month"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 447960.0,
      "end_time": 449640.0,
      "text": "to show the amount of water"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 449640.0,
      "end_time": 453920.0,
      "text": "falling on every small part of the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 453920.0,
      "end_time": 457240.0,
      "text": "And you see the monsoons moving around the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 457240.0,
      "end_time": 461720.0,
      "text": "and the planet almost appears to have a heartbeat."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 461720.0,
      "end_time": 466920.0,
      "text": "And all of this only became possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 466920.0,
      "end_time": 468720.0,
      "text": "within my lifetime"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 468720.0,
      "end_time": 472640.0,
      "text": "to see this is where we are living."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 472640.0,
      "end_time": 475760.0,
      "text": "We have enough water."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 475760.0,
      "end_time": 481280.0,
      "text": "This is a map of where we grow our food in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 481280.0,
      "end_time": 487760.0,
      "text": "This is the areas that we will rely on most for rice and maize and corn."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 487760.0,
      "end_time": 490640.0,
      "text": "People worry that there won&#39;t be enough food, but we know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 490640.0,
      "end_time": 495440.0,
      "text": "if we just ate less meat and fed less of the crops to animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 495440.0,
      "end_time": 497880.0,
      "text": "there is enough food for everybody"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 497880.0,
      "end_time": 504120.0,
      "text": "as long as we think of ourselves as one group of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 504120.0,
      "end_time": 507280.0,
      "text": "And we also know"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 507280.0,
      "end_time": 509360.0,
      "text": "about what we do"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 509360.0,
      "end_time": 513480.0,
      "text": "so terribly badly nowadays."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 513480.0,
      "end_time": 519480.0,
      "text": "You will have seen this map of the world before."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 519480.0,
      "end_time": 521440.0,
      "text": "This is the map"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 521440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524840.0,
      "text": "produced by taking satellite images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 524840.0,
      "end_time": 527640.0,
      "text": "if you remember those satellites around the planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 527640.0,
      "end_time": 531240.0,
      "text": "in the very first slide I showed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 531240.0,
      "end_time": 535720.0,
      "text": "and producing an image of what the Earth looks like at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 535720.0,
      "end_time": 537640.0,
      "text": "When you normally see that map,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 537640.0,
      "end_time": 542160.0,
      "text": "on a normal map, the kind of map that most of you will be used to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 542160.0,
      "end_time": 546120.0,
      "text": "you think you are seeing a map of where people live."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 546120.0,
      "end_time": 549320.0,
      "text": "Where the lights are shining up is where people live."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 549320.0,
      "end_time": 553720.0,
      "text": "But here, on this image of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 553720.0,
      "end_time": 557320.0,
      "text": "remember we&#39;ve stretched the map again."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 557320.0,
      "end_time": 562480.0,
      "text": "Everywhere has the same density of people on this map."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 562480.0,
      "end_time": 564680.0,
      "text": "If an area doesn&#39;t have people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 564680.0,
      "end_time": 566600.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve shrunk it away"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 566600.0,
      "end_time": 568160.0,
      "text": "to make it disappear."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 568160.0,
      "end_time": 570320.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re showing everybody"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 570320.0,
      "end_time": 573320.0,
      "text": "with equal prominence."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 573320.0,
      "end_time": 576640.0,
      "text": "Now, the lights no longer show you where people are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 576640.0,
      "end_time": 579120.0,
      "text": "because people are everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 579120.0,
      "end_time": 581080.0,
      "text": "Now the lights on the map,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 581080.0,
      "end_time": 584080.0,
      "text": "the lights in London, the lights in Cairo, the lights in Tokyo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 584080.0,
      "end_time": 587040.0,
      "text": "the lights on the Eastern Seaboard of the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 587040.0,
      "end_time": 590000.0,
      "text": "the lights show you where people live"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 590000.0,
      "end_time": 593160.0,
      "text": "who are so profligate with energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 593160.0,
      "end_time": 595680.0,
      "text": "that they can afford"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 595680.0,
      "end_time": 597240.0,
      "text": "to spend money"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 597240.0,
      "end_time": 600720.0,
      "text": "powering lights to shine up into the sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 600720.0,
      "end_time": 604840.0,
      "text": "so satellites can draw an image like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 604840.0,
      "end_time": 607720.0,
      "text": "And the areas that are dark on the map"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 607720.0,
      "end_time": 612400.0,
      "text": "are either areas where people do not have access to that much energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 612400.0,
      "end_time": 614520.0,
      "text": "or areas where people do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 614520.0,
      "end_time": 619960.0,
      "text": "but they have learned to stop shining the light up into the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 619960.0,
      "end_time": 623520.0,
      "text": "And if I could show you this map animated over time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 623520.0,
      "end_time": 627120.0,
      "text": "you would see that Tokyo has actually become darker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 627120.0,
      "end_time": 630880.0,
      "text": "because ever since the tsunami in Japan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 630880.0,
      "end_time": 633320.0,
      "text": "Japan has had to rely on a quarter less electricity"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 633320.0,
      "end_time": 637240.0,
      "text": "because it turned the nuclear power stations off."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 637240.0,
      "end_time": 639400.0,
      "text": "And the world didn&#39;t end."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 639400.0,
      "end_time": 641600.0,
      "text": "You just shone less light"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 641600.0,
      "end_time": 645320.0,
      "text": "up into the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 645320.0,
      "end_time": 648320.0,
      "text": "There are a huge number"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 648320.0,
      "end_time": 651880.0,
      "text": "of good news stories in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 651880.0,
      "end_time": 655320.0,
      "text": "Infant mortality is falling"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 655320.0,
      "end_time": 659920.0,
      "text": "and has been falling at an incredible rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 659920.0,
      "end_time": 662240.0,
      "text": "A few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 662240.0,
      "end_time": 666200.0,
      "text": "the number of babies dying in their first year of life in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 666200.0,
      "end_time": 671600.0,
      "text": "fell by five percent in just one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 671600.0,
      "end_time": 674120.0,
      "text": "More children are going to school"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 674120.0,
      "end_time": 676760.0,
      "text": "and learning to read and write"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 676760.0,
      "end_time": 679600.0,
      "text": "and getting connected to the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 679600.0,
      "end_time": 682640.0,
      "text": "and going on to go to university"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 682640.0,
      "end_time": 686560.0,
      "text": "than ever before at an incredible rate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 686560.0,
      "end_time": 692040.0,
      "text": "and the highest number of young people going to university in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 692040.0,
      "end_time": 695160.0,
      "text": "are women, not men."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 695160.0,
      "end_time": 699080.0,
      "text": "I can give you good news story after good news story"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 699080.0,
      "end_time": 701720.0,
      "text": "about what is getting better in the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 701720.0,
      "end_time": 705880.0,
      "text": "but we tend to concentrate"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 705880.0,
      "end_time": 708640.0,
      "text": "on the bad news that is immediate."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 708640.0,
      "end_time": 713160.0,
      "text": "Rebecca Solnit, I think, put it brilliantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 713160.0,
      "end_time": 718520.0,
      "text": "when she explained: &quot;The accretion of incremental, imperceptible changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 718520.0,
      "end_time": 721360.0,
      "text": "which can constitute progress and which render our era"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 721360.0,
      "end_time": 724200.0,
      "text": "dramatically different from the past&quot; --"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 724200.0,
      "end_time": 727640.0,
      "text": "the past was much more stable --"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 727640.0,
      "end_time": 732640.0,
      "text": "&quot;a contrast obscured by the undramatic nature of gradual transformation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 732640.0,
      "end_time": 736320.0,
      "text": "punctuated by occasional tumult.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 736320.0,
      "end_time": 739440.0,
      "text": "Occasionally, terrible things happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 739440.0,
      "end_time": 742200.0,
      "text": "You are shown those terrible things"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 742200.0,
      "end_time": 745880.0,
      "text": "on the news every night of the week."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 745880.0,
      "end_time": 749880.0,
      "text": "You are not told about the population slowing down."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 749880.0,
      "end_time": 752920.0,
      "text": "You are not told about the world becoming more connected."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 752920.0,
      "end_time": 756600.0,
      "text": "You are not told about the incredible improvements in understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 756600.0,
      "end_time": 759760.0,
      "text": "You are not told about how we are learning to begin"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 759760.0,
      "end_time": 762240.0,
      "text": "to waste less and consume less."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 762240.0,
      "end_time": 764360.0,
      "text": "This is my last map."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 764360.0,
      "end_time": 766760.0,
      "text": "On this map, we have taken the seas"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 766760.0,
      "end_time": 769480.0,
      "text": "and the oceans out."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 769480.0,
      "end_time": 771520.0,
      "text": "Now you are just looking"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 771520.0,
      "end_time": 775400.0,
      "text": "at about 7.4 billion people"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 775400.0,
      "end_time": 779240.0,
      "text": "with the map drawn in proportion to those people."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 779240.0,
      "end_time": 781320.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re looking at over a billion in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 781320.0,
      "end_time": 784160.0,
      "text": "and you can see the largest city in the world in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 784160.0,
      "end_time": 787080.0,
      "text": "but you do not know its name."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 787080.0,
      "end_time": 788960.0,
      "text": "You can see that India"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 788960.0,
      "end_time": 791640.0,
      "text": "is in the center of this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 791640.0,
      "end_time": 794960.0,
      "text": "You can see that Europe is on the edge."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 794960.0,
      "end_time": 798040.0,
      "text": "And we in Exeter today"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 798040.0,
      "end_time": 801000.0,
      "text": "are on the far edge of the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 801000.0,
      "end_time": 804000.0,
      "text": "We are on a tiny scrap of rock"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 804000.0,
      "end_time": 805720.0,
      "text": "off Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 805720.0,
      "end_time": 808360.0,
      "text": "which contains less than one percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 808360.0,
      "end_time": 810400.0,
      "text": "of the world&#39;s adults,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 810400.0,
      "end_time": 812960.0,
      "text": "and less than half a percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 812960.0,
      "end_time": 815640.0,
      "text": "of the world&#39;s children."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 815640.0,
      "end_time": 820280.0,
      "text": "We are living in a stabilizing world, an urbanizing world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 820280.0,
      "end_time": 822280.0,
      "text": "an aging world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 822280.0,
      "end_time": 824440.0,
      "text": "a connecting world."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 824440.0,
      "end_time": 828720.0,
      "text": "There are many, many things to be frightened about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 828720.0,
      "end_time": 833960.0,
      "text": "but there is no need for us to fear each other as much as we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 833960.0,
      "end_time": 838960.0,
      "text": "and we need to see that we are now living in a new world."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 838960.0,
      "end_time": 840200.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 840200.0,
      "end_time": 850200.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}